//stacking order//

stacking order will have no effect unless its postioned relative static or absolute.
so if you want an items to be stacked but dont want to take it out of the document flow use position 


//hamburger menue animations wont work on ios//

i implemented kevin powells svg hamburger menu animation and it didnt work on ios devices.
some browsers can apply stylesd to the y and x of svgs
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R00QiudbD4Y&t=1663s&ab_channel=KevinPowell

solution:use transform translate instead. 

